---
export const pagetitle = "Home"; // or any title you want

import Welcome from '../components/Welcome.astro';
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout>
    <p class="spaced-paragraph">
        Welcome to your cloud’s personal IT department. Our goal is to “Marie Kondo” your cloud email, drive, and photos.<br />
        <br />
        Do you want to save on paying for more cloud storage?<br />
        <br />
        Do you miss important emails in your cluttered mailbox?<br />
        <br />
        Can’t receive emails or can’t share photos cause you’ve hit your storage limit?<br />
        <br />
        Just plain tired of how messy your cloud email, photos, and drive are?<br />
        <br />
        Or got other cloud problems?<br />
        <br />
        Then you’ve come to the right place! We want to help you.
    </p>

    <div class="two-sections">
      <section class="left-section">
        <h2>Cleaner Cloud Service</h2>
        <!-- Add content for Cleaner Cloud Service here -->
        <p>Professional help to organize, clean, and optimize your cloud storage and email.</p>
      </section>
      <section class="right-section">
        <h2>Cleaner Cloud Suite</h2>
        <!-- Add content for Cleaner Cloud Suite here -->
        <p>Tools and resources for you to manage your cloud storage and email on your own.</p>
      </section>
    </div>

    <style>
      .spaced-paragraph {
        line-height: 1.6;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .two-sections {
        display: flex;
        gap: 2rem;
        margin-top: 2rem;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: stretch;
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 1600px;
        margin-left: auto;
        margin-right: auto;
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }
      .left-section, .right-section {
        flex: 1 1 0;
        background: #f8f8f8;
        padding: 3rem 2.5rem;
        border-radius: 10px;
        box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.04);
        min-width: 0; /* Allow to shrink */
        font-size: 1.15rem;
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }
      .left-section h2, .right-section h2 {
        text-align: center;
      }
      @media (max-width: 1000px) {
        .two-sections {
          flex-direction: column;
          align-items: center;
          width: 100%;
          max-width: 100vw;
        }
        .left-section, .right-section {
          max-width: 95vw;
          min-width: 0;
          padding: 2rem 1rem;
        }
      }
    </style>
</Layout>
